{"tid":1178652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[辛鳩苦]家家有本難唸的經！","createTime":"2019-05-30T14:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T04:17:25.000Z","uid":153493,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37b8e621c30de97d84bfe5deac78e7c022896294","tid":1178652,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"人大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈黎愈發覺屋企人<br />\n係老屎忽/食古不化/岸撚柒鳩/癡撚線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係香港大是大非問題嘅事<br />\n好憎佢地老一派覺得搵食 有工返最緊要<br />\n現實係重要但有時候係講緊放手一搏去改變<br />\n窮則變 變則通 唔去改變 點有意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋磚:屋企廚房嘅甲由愈黎愈撚猖狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚十點未到已經可以出黎行街<br />\n然後我老豆都仲可以打開碗碟櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話透下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗:你愈老愈撚唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明白點撚解佢仲可以用自己濕鳩嘅一套做事<br />\n一成不變 牛皮燈籠 自相矛盾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我或多或少討厭自己出生環境<br />\n但同時幾感恩知足嘅<br />\n大把人嘅屋企條件更差<br />\n自己不外如是<br />\n亦都明係自己廢 無撚用 同懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話真係介意自己屋企人唔有錢<br />\n始終香港地大把基層日日掙扎求存緊<br />\n自己比上不足 比下有餘<br />\n但佢地窮撚到仆街嘅係思想<br />\n好撚不思進取到一個唔識講嘅地步了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們身同感受嘅話就會明<br />\n最憎屋企人安於現況<br />\n日日只諗吃喝玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺低一個自己覺得生活係屋企<br />\n好辛鳩苦同好撚煩燥不安嘅事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌我明你呀樓豬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾廢柴唔識逆向思維多角度思考"},{"pid":"e3f7e43d1890189edb8d647ed77e545839eb1fa6","tid":1178652,"uid":206828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊加油"},{"pid":"efe1386d0f21bbc1803be3e40271173c6bfd7f91","tid":1178652,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3f7e43d1890189edb8d647ed77e545839eb1fa6","tid":1178652,"uid":206828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"巴定絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講以為我識你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定真係識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共勉G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e6be5f6cb8e857d10059d1e90c16ee17b0b440","tid":1178652,"uid":207646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"唉我屋企都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未食完嘅餸就咁放過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話等到第二日當晏就食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我都唔敢係屋企食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8624fe03e2f8ee5a3c8eb8a28fe032dbf2dc7f","tid":1178652,"uid":91918,"like":1,"